    "body": "### Problem\n\n[https://neovim.io/doc/user/nvim/#nvim](https://neovim.io/doc/user/nvim/#nvim)\n\nRestart Nvim, your existing Vim config will be loaded.\n`:restart`\n\nI'm running neovim 0.11.5 on windows installed via chocolatey. \n\nI get error E492...\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nnvim \n:restart\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nRestart nvim\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\n0.11.5\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nUnsure\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nWindows 11 Home, 26200.7623\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nPowershell\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nunsure\n\n### Installation\n\nchocolatey",
